invalid type: string "# Employee Leave Policy\n\n## Annual Leave\n\n- Full-time employees receive **21 paid annual leave days** every year.\n- Annual leave requests must be submitted at least **5 working days** before the leave date.\n- Approval from the employee's direct manager is required.\n- Employees may carry forward a maximum of **5 unused annual leave days** to the following year.\n\n---\n